<plot>LET ME GET MY COAT! [Waar is mijn jas?] Netherlands, 2004 In 1980, Wim Verstappen and Paul Verhoeven, Holland's best-known film makers, were interviewed by film writer Ruud den Drijver. The film makers Dirk Rijneke and Mildred van Leeuwaarden followed this humorous encounter with the camera. A hilarious film with spicy statements; a document that provides a unique glimpse of the Dutch film world in the 1980s.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?645570</url></doc>
